Configuration
=============



Usage
=====

To use this module, you need to:

1. Go to *Repair > Configuration > Settings*.

Bug Tracker
===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues <https://github.com/OCA/repair/issues>`_.
In case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.
If you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed
`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/repair/issues/new?body=module:%20base_repair_config%0Aversion:%2018.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.

Do not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.

